{"tid":370902,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"(好戲保證) 習近平點名大讚《打死不離3父女》","createTime":"2017-08-23T10:01:28.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-23T10:24:35.000Z","uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"6c3895a6f5c57aca90445b2c154db2962ceee9d6","tid":370902,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-23T10:01:28.000Z","msg":"習近平點名大讚《打死不離3父女》, 並希望更多類似電影在中國上映.<br />\n<br />\n《打死不離3父女》明天香港上映.<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://chinafilminsider.com/xi-jinping-tells-modi-loves-dangal-want-movies-china/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fchinafilminsider.com%2Fxi-jinping-tells-modi-loves-dangal-want-movies-china%2F&d=ox5U%2F7G%2FhUOIrXJuGdZiwEbWhtBCnEJYRTWbVbFBOac%3D&h=b04ef77d\" target=\"_blank\">http://chinafilminsider.com/xi-jinping-tells-modi-loves-dangal-want-movies-china/</a><br />\n<br />\nBollywood&rsquo;s Dangal, already the highest earning non-Hollywood foreign film in Chinese history, earned another important Chinese fan over the weekend &mdash; China&rsquo;s President Xi Jinping.<br />\n<br />\nSpeaking to his Indian counterpart Prime Minister Narendra Modi at a summit in Kazakhstan on Friday, Xi said he &lsquo;loved&rsquo; the Aamir Khan-starrer, and that he wanted to see more such movies in China in the future, India&rsquo;s Foreign Secretary S Jaishankar told Indian media."},{"pid":"24d79a4fb24b100f524d576be6e8288d1b959f84","tid":370902,"uid":99364,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-23T10:06:12.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"cd8e125597f736b680e290fba9de91e05bc7aa70","tid":370902,"uid":78620,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-23T10:10:37.000Z","msg":"習近平想同印度打完場波<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"01f0b09ca03cf62e88ed1ab4b56d9ea2c8679cbe","tid":370902,"uid":8441,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-23T10:19:05.000Z","msg":"印度出維尼宣傳片都無事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.